ComicInfo.Summary:
Cherry Hammer & Becky inspect the crime scene where their colleague was murdered -- a fabulous yacht belonging to one of the world's richest men, Zackary May -- and recreate the events of that terrible night. Meanwhile, Katchoo is called into action to meet with May and finds a surprise at her door.
